{"tid":1544513,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦lag機會係咩問題？","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T12:54:00.000Z","uid":18721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a3d42b8081574687f1c93b59182da04af4b42b","tid":1544513,"uid":18721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"想請問咁多位巴打<br />\n小弟電腦依個星期開始就lag機<br />\n佢個lag法就好似以前睇老翻咁 定一定再追返個幾秒咁<br />\n睇片聽歌都係你會見到佢追返個幾秒 飛帶咁飛<br />\n但係打LOL入左game又唔會有影響<br />\n另外會見到mouse係會行行下慢左 或者停左係到<br />\n再追返去你郁個路徑<br />\n請問會係啲咩問題 同點解決？<br />\n我試過用防毒去掃又冇事 磁碟重組都係咁<br />\n<br />\n想請教下巴打們可以點解決<br />\n大約個情況係咁<br />\n但係唔run stress test都會出現依個情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/358082080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F358082080&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=85fa5f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/358082080</a>"},{"pid":"93088c1215a94a3249a3335fe509384e78c1c50b","tid":1544513,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18e9ec5a3e8a70bf157ac9c61e0e7dd66ad0c2a3","tid":1544513,"uid":2734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"咩都可能係 唯有逐樣試 <br />\n開住task manager 睇下cpu ram hdd usage 出事個時有咩變化"},{"pid":"edf18a38a7408a2dd753d0aa18a4eac5dc8e921d","tid":1544513,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n好撚好聽<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=22e322c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJuEF0r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJuEF0r.gif&h=a8c24eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=831b769b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"9ee96c5a3900cc15579fbdd100514ee7e64d6d38","tid":1544513,"uid":18721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e9ec5a3e8a70bf157ac9c61e0e7dd66ad0c2a3","tid":1544513,"uid":2734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"咩都可能係 唯有逐樣試 <br />\n開住task manager 睇下cpu ra